
                                 DRBD
                                ======
                           by Philipp Reisner
                           and Lars Ellenberg
                     LINBIT Information Technologies

Reference documentation is included in the documentation directory.

Please refer to the web pages at

  http://www.drbd.org/
  http://www.drbd.org/docs/introduction/

to find maintained information.

Because open DRBD just support A,B,C,protocol,and those protocol will blocked IO on Application.
This branch add a S protocol. 
the S protocol is full async protocol to drbd.
and S protocol never blocked the IO process on ther master node.
